tagline.en: SuperONE, deeply ploughing years of technical specialist and aesthetic flow in the graphene field, continuing to focus on the contribution of graphene ecosystem.
tagline.cn: SuperONE，深耕石墨烯领域多年的技术流和审美流，持续专注为石墨烯生态贡献力量。

introduce.en: We deeply ploughing years of technical specialist and aesthetic flow in the graphene field, continuing to focus on the contribution of graphene ecosystem. The SuperONE project founder (community ID: crazybit) is deeping involved in the BitShares community, also responsible for one of the BitShares witness nodes and has in-depth research on the kernel of graphene. We have two products currently, one is BitShares wallet named SuperONE(https://superone.io), another is EOS LIVE(https://eos.live), which is the first product and information aggregation platform for EOS community.
introduce.cn: 我们是最早期的区块链技术狂热爱好者，深耕石墨烯领域多年的技术流和审美流，持续专注为石墨烯生态贡献力量。SuperONE 项目发起人（社区 ID：crazybit) 是 BitShares 社区的资深参与者，同时也是 BitShares 见证人节点之一的负责人，对石墨烯底层有深入的研究。目前我们上线了两个产品，一是 BitShares 钱包 SuperONE（https://superone.io），二是 EOS 社区首个产品与资讯聚合平台 EOS LIVE（https://eos.live）。
